name: cartola
description:
digital painting based on Cartola, a brazilian singer, composer and poet, one of the major figures in samba.

"let me go,
i must wander.
i'll go around, searching,
laugh so i won't cry.
if someone asks for me,
tell them i'll only be back
after i find myself"
 - Cartola (1908-1980)

3648x2736
